Use the standard library
This is how to select_words of s and n:
   Remember that words is []
   Remember that current is ""
   Remember that i is 0

   Do this s's length times:
      Remember that ch is item i in s
      When ch is item 0 in " ", then:
         When current's length is more than 0, then:
            When current's length is n, then:
               Add words to current
            End when
            Remember that current is ""
         End when
      But, if not:
         Add current to ch
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   When current's length is more than 0, then:
      When current's length is n, then:
         Add words to current
      End when
   End when

   The answer is words
